342
00:25:23.083 --> 00:25:24.083
90 seconds ago

343
00:25:24.333 --> 00:25:26.333
Margaret. over here!

344
00:25:27.333 --> 00:25:29.000
Call the police and

345
00:25:29.167 --> 00:25:31.583
We have to catch him...
Maria needs help.

346
00:25:31.750 --> 00:25:32.917
Go right now.

347
00:25:33.083 --> 00:25:35.917
