484
00:35:07.333 --> 00:35:09.500
Go change your clothes. We have to get out of here.

485
00:35:09.917 --> 00:35:11.083
Let's go!  Hurry up!

486
00:35:11.583 --> 00:35:12.750
Sorry!

487
00:35:13.833 --> 00:35:16.167
