What lies ahead is too painful to watch.

507
00:37:52.667 --> 00:37:55.333
After Hugo showed it to me.
I ended up getting involved.

508
00:38:00.000 --> 00:38:02.500
Interrogation on the VIVO 10

509
00:38:14.833 --> 00:38:16.217
Stop the sedatives.
